{"thag2.21:0.1":"Theragatha 2.21 ","thag2.21:0.2":"Dukanipata ","thag2.21:0.3":"Tatiyavagga ","thag2.21:0.4":"Uttarattheragatha ","thag2.21:1.1":"“Khandha maya parinnata, ","thag2.21:1.2":"tanha me susamuhata; ","thag2.21:1.3":"Bhavita mama bojjhanga, ","thag2.21:1.4":"patto me asavakkhayo. ","thag2.21:2.1":"Soham khandhe parinnaya, ","thag2.21:2.2":"abbahitvana jalinim; ","thag2.21:2.3":"Bhavayitvana bojjhange, ","thag2.21:2.4":"nibbayissam anasavo”ti. ","thag2.21:2.5":"… Uttaro thero …. "}